des:
SCLink app products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to SCLink app products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our SCLink app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register account in our SCLink app;
(3). You need to have some SCLink app devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our SCLink app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in “SCLink Smarthome”skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search “SCLink Smarthome” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of “SCLink Smarthome”, and you'll be navigated to “SCLink Smarthome” login page;
(9). Input your Replace your App name account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off switch.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
